research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md:67:| `shared_stacked_product_key_expert_jumprelu` | `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(x)} α_i^sh b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E_pk(r_1(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^τ(r_1(x))} β_{e,j} b_{e,j} + Σ_{e∈E_pk(r_1(x))} Σ_{m∈S_e^τ(r_2(x))} γ_{e,m} b_{e,m}` | candidate | shared coarse 子库后接两次 residual PK expert cleanup；第二次 cleanup 复用同一批静态 expert 子库，只增加 expert-local 残差求系数，不引入动态字典，最终仍是静态库有限加权和 | 直接兼容 |
research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md:68:| `shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu` | `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(h(x))} α_i^sh b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E_pk(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^τ(r_sh(x))} α_{e,j} b_{e,j}` | candidate | low-rank shared bottleneck 只改变 shared coarse 与 PK routing 的打分链路，expert cleanup 仍落在静态 expert 子库上；最终仍是静态库有限加权和 | 直接兼容 |
research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md:69:| `dual_shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu` | `x_hat = Σ_{s=1..2} Σ_{i∈S_s(h(x))} α_{s,i}^sh b_{s,i}^sh + Σ_{e∈E_pk(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^τ(r_sh(x))} α_{e,j} b_{e,j}` | candidate | 两个 low-rank shared coarse 子库负责更厚的主干，PK router 仍只在静态 expert 子库间选择，expert cleanup 保持 full-expert JumpReLU；最终仍是静态库有限加权和 | 直接兼容 |
research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md:70:| `dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` | `x_hat = Σ_{s=1..2} Σ_{i∈S_s(x)} α_{s,i}^sh b_{s,i}^sh + Σ_{e∈E_pk(r_sh(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^τ(r_sh(x))} α_{e,j} b_{e,j}` | candidate | 两个 always-on shared 静态子库负责更厚的 coarse 主干，product-key router 只在静态 expert 子库间选择，JumpReLU 只改变 expert 内局部 support；最终仍是静态库有限加权和 | 直接兼容 |
research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md:71:| `residual_dual_shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` | `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_1(x)} α_i^{sh,1} b_i^{sh,1} + Σ_{j∈S_2(r_1(x))} α_j^{sh,2} b_j^{sh,2} + Σ_{e∈E_pk(r_2(x))} Σ_{m∈S_e^τ(r_2(x))} α_{e,m} b_{e,m}` | candidate | 两个 shared 静态子库不是并行竞争同一 top-k，而是先后在 residual 上串联清理主干，再接 PK expert cleanup；仍只访问静态子库并做有限加权和 | 直接兼容 |
